Fix ncurses Makefile generation on GitHub Actions macOS runners.

Replace >> append redirects with write-to-temp + concatenate pattern.
Pre-process subset values via tr to replace + with spaces before
passing to AWK, bypassing a gawk gsub issue on CI where neither
gsub("[+]",...) nor gsub(/[+]/,...) replaces + with space.

